2.8,22.9 71.5,22.9"></polygon></svg> <span class="sr-only">(opens new window)</span></span></a>（以先到者为准），就会有效地冻结。</p> <p><code>SCHED_RR</code> 是除 Windows 之外的所有操作系统的默认值。 一旦 libuv 能够有效地分发 IOCP 句柄而不会导致大量性能损失，则 Windows 将更改为 <code>SCHED_RR</code>。</p> <p><code>cluster.schedulingPolicy</code> 也可以通过 <code>NODE_CLUSTER_SCHED_POLICY</code> 环境变量设置。 有效值为 <code>'rr'</code> 和 <code>'none'</code>。</p> <h3 id="cluster-settings"><a href="#cluster-settings" class="header-anchor">#</a> <code>cluster.settings</code><a href="http://nodejs.cn/api-v12/cluster.html#clustersettings" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">#<span><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false" x="0px" y="0px" viewBox="0 0 100 100" width="15" height="15" class="icon outbound"><path fill="currentColor" d="M18.8,85.1h56l0,0c2.2,0,4-1.8,4-4v-32h-8v28h-48v-48h28v-8h-32l0,0c-2.2,0-4,1.8-4,4v56C14.8,83.3,16.6,85.1,18.8,85.1z"></path> <polygon fill="currentColor" points="45.7,48.7 51.3,54.3 77.2,28.5 77.2,37.2 85.2,37.2 85.2,14.9 62.8,14.9 62.8,22.9 71.5,22.9"></polygon></svg> <span class="sr-only">(opens new window)</span></span></a></h3> <p><a href="http://nodejs.cn/api-v12/cluster/cluster_settings.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">中英对照<span><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false" x="0px" y="0px" viewBox="0 0 100 100" width="15" height="15" class="icon outbound"><path fill="currentColor" d="M18.8,85.1h56l0,0c2.2,0,4-1.8,4-4v-32h-8v28h-48v-48h28v-8h-32l0,0c-2.2,0-4,1.8-4,4v56C14.8,83.3,16.6,85.1,18.8,85.1z"></path> <polygon fill="currentColor" points="45.7,48.7 51.3,54.3 77.2,28.5 77.2,37.2 85.2,37.2 85.2,14.9 62.8,14.9 62.8,22.9 71.5,22.9"></polygon></svg> <span class="sr-only">(opens new window)</span></span></a></p> <ul><li><a href="http://url.nodejs.cn/jzn6Ao" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><Object><span><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false" x="0px" y="0px" viewBox="0 0 100 100" wi