> <span class="sr-only">(opens new window)</span></span></Function></a> 设置工作进程的检查器端口。 这可以是数字，也可以是不带参数并返回数字的函数。 默认情况下，每个工作进程都有自己的端口，从主进程的 <code>process.debugPort</code> 开始递增。</li> <li><code>windowsHide</code> <a href="http://url.nodejs.cn/jFbvuT" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><boolean><span><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false" x="0px" y="0px" viewBox="0 0 100 100" width="15" height="15" class="icon outbound"><path fill="currentColor" d="M18.8,85.1h56l0,0c2.2,0,4-1.8,4-4v-32h-8v28h-48v-48h28v-8h-32l0,0c-2.2,0-4,1.8-4,4v56C14.8,83.3,16.6,85.1,18.8,85.1z"></path> <polygon fill="currentColor" points="45.7,48.7 51.3,54.3 77.2,28.5 77.2,37.2 85.2,37.2 85.2,14.9 62.8,14.9 62.8,22.9 71.5,22.9"></polygon></svg> <span class="sr-only">(opens new window)</span></span></boolean></a> 隐藏通常在 Windows 系统上创建的衍生进程控制台窗口。 <strong>默认值:</strong> <code>false</code>。</li></ul></li></ul> <p>调用 <a href="http://nodejs.cn/api-v12/cluster.html#cluster_cluster_setupmaster_settings" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><code>.setupMaster()</code><span><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false" x="0px" y="0px" viewBox="0 0 100 100" width="15" height="15" class="icon outbound"><path fill="currentColor" d="M18.8,85.1h56l0,0c2.2,0,4-1.8,4-4v-32h-8v28h-48v-48h28v-8h-32l0,0c-2.2,0-4,1.8-4,4v56C14.8,83.3,16.6,85.1,18.8,85.1z"></path> <polygon fill="currentColor" points="45.7,48.7 51.3,54.3 77.2,28.5 77.2,37.2 85.2,37.2 85.2,14.9 62.8,14.9 62.8,22.9 71.5,22.9"></polygon></svg> <span class="sr-only">(opens new window)</span></span></a>（或 <a href="http://nodejs.cn/api-v12/cluster.html#cluster_cluster_fork_env" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><code>.fork()</code><span><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false" x="0px" y="0px" viewBox="0 0 100 100" width="15" height="15" class="icon outbound"><path fill="currentColor" d="M18.8,85.1h56l0,0c2.2,0,4-1.8,4-4v-32h-8v28h-48v-48h28v-8h